text.section:
A citation issued under this title shall include:
The name and address of the person charged;
The nature of the violation;
The location and time of the violation;
The amount of the civil penalty;
The manner, location, and time in which the civil penalty may be paid;
The cited person's right to elect to stand trial for the violation; and
A warning that failure to pay the civil penalty or to contest liability in a timely manner in accordance with the citation:
Is an admission of liability; and
May result in an entry of a default judgment that may include the civil penalty, court costs, and administrative expenses.
